how are we doing sub: Ang inyong mga opinyon tungkol sa inyong mga karanasan sa Webmaker ay tunay na importante sa amin. Sa katunayan, ang inyong feedback ay ang una naming tinitignan sa pag plaplano namin ng hinaharap para sa ikabubuti ng site. Nakikiusap po kami sa inyong oras para sabihin sa amin kung ano ang mga nagustuhan nyo tungkol sa site, ano ang mga hindi gumagana ayon sa inaasahan nyo at kung ano ang sa tingin nyo na mas tamang gawin.

Tag your work with #makerparty: The Maker Party relies on people like you to help teach others how to create on the web. Why not throw your own party? You don't have to have to be a pro to do it either. From groups of two to groups of hundreds, we have guides to help you plan for any size party where you can teach or learn with your peers.

Creating the web is the heart of our wor: Creating the web is the heart of our work. We build tools like Thimble, X-Ray Goggles and Popcorn Maker that allow people to create amazing content while peeking under the hood of the internet, getting familiar with all the moving parts and getting their hands dirty with foundational elements like HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
